    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed or scoped. Seven factors achieved level 3 against required level 4 at MRL 5; model form and model inputs factors show the largest gaps. Monte Carlo UQ results demonstrate 90th-percentile coverage of experimental data at all 5 operating points under the current solver configuration. The assessment team accepted the submission on the basis of the Monte Carlo coverage result and the overall validation evidence package, noting that remaining credibility gaps are documented for post-market surveillance follow-up.",
